metadata.name: Wonderful Dream
metadata.description:
Immerse yourself into wondreful dream of Olivia where you take any shape or form. 

Here you will sail down this beautiful river on a whale-boat while dolphin will envelop you in a pleasant sea wave and you will be plunged into deep, fabulous dream.

The castle almost fell asleep and the time for fantasies, imagination and magic began.

Dolphins whales and orcas are having fun in the water, fairies are keeping this dream magical and vibrant.

While gliding through the clouds on her scarled sailed ship Olivia is trying to catch a fish that grants wishes.

Pegasus is keeping her safe from harm, even if she doesn't know about it.

Monkey that is descending into dream also represents Olivia, being so curious and mischievous.

Olivia really wants to get to the house, which is so far away, because her parents live there, and she misses them a lot.

Phoenix represents light, warms and sun, and when it turns to ashes - Olivia will wake up.
